{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1332,"text":"So I tried to do a small good thing for my wife."},{"time":5417,"text":"It makes me to stand here,"},{"time":7779,"text":"the fame, the money I got out of it."},{"time":10433,"text":"So what I did, I'd gone back to my early marriage days."},{"time":13966,"text":"What you did in the early marriage days,"},{"time":15895,"text":"you tried to impress your wife. I did the same."},{"time":18714,"text":"On that occasion, I found my wife"},{"time":21549,"text":"carrying something like this."},{"time":23720,"text":"I saw. \"What is that?\" I asked."},{"time":25960,"text":"My wife replied, \"None of your business.\""},{"time":29229,"text":"Then, being her husband, I ran behind her"},{"time":31320,"text":"and saw she had a nasty rag cloth."},{"time":32856,"text":"I don't even use that cloth to clean my two-wheeler."},{"time":35824,"text":"Then I understood this -- adapting that unhygienic method"},{"time":38626,"text":"to manage her period days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40927,"text":"Then I immediately asked her, why are you [using] that unhygienic method?"},{"time":42712,"text":"She replied, I also know about [sanitary pads],"},{"time":46250,"text":"but myself and my sisters, if they start using that,"},{"time":49325,"text":"we have to cut our family milk budget."},{"time":51909,"text":"Then I was shocked. What is the connection between"},{"time":53228,"text":"using a sanitary pad and a milk budget?"},{"time":54693,"text":"And it's called affordability."},{"time":57183,"text":"I tried to impress my new wife by offering her a packet of sanitary pads."},{"time":61505,"text":"I went to a local shop, I tried to buy her a sanitary pad packet."},{"time":64666,"text":"That fellow looks left and right,"},{"time":66259,"text":"and spreads a newspaper, rolls it into the newspaper,"},{"time":68700,"text":"gives it to me like a banned item, something like that."},{"time":72484,"text":"I don't know why. I did not ask for a condom."},{"time":76283,"text":"Then I took that pad. I want to see that. What is inside it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":80404,"text":"The very first time, at the age of 29,"},{"time":84359,"text":"that day I am touching the sanitary pad, first ever."},{"time":86434,"text":"I must know: How many of the guys here have touched a sanitary pad?"},{"time":91494,"text":"They are not going to touch that, because it's not your matter."},{"time":96134,"text":"Then I thought to myself, white substance, made of cotton --"},{"time":99362,"text":"oh my God, that guy is just using a penny value of raw material --"},{"time":102703,"text":"inside they are selling for pounds, dollars."},{"time":105257,"text":"Why not make a local sanitary pad for my new wife?"},{"time":110071,"text":"That's how all this started, but after making a sanitary pad,"},{"time":113080,"text":"where can I check it?"},{"time":114476,"text":"It's not like I can just check it in the lab."},{"time":117702,"text":"I need a woman volunteer. Where can I get one in India?"},{"time":120652,"text":"Even in Bangalore you won't get [one], in India."},{"time":124232,"text":"So only problem: the only available victim is my wife."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129636,"text":"Then I made a sanitary pad and handed it to Shanti -- my wife's name is Shanti."},{"time":134236,"text":"\"Close your eyes. Whatever I give,"},{"time":135540,"text":"it will be not a diamond pendant"},{"time":137152,"text":"not a diamond ring, even a chocolate,"},{"time":138701,"text":"I will give you a surprise with a lot of tinsel paper rolled up with it."},{"time":142205,"text":"Close your eyes.\""},{"time":144156,"text":"Because I tried to make it intimate."},{"time":147230,"text":"Because it's an arranged marriage, not a love marriage."},{"time":150441,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":152960,"text":"So one day she said, openly, I'm not going to support this research."},{"time":156539,"text":"Then other victims, they got into my sisters."},{"time":159655,"text":"But even sisters, wives, they're not ready to support in the research."},{"time":163052,"text":"That's why I am always jealous with the saints in India."},{"time":166094,"text":"They are having a lot of women volunteers around them."},{"time":169653,"text":"Why I am not getting [any]?"},{"time":171349,"text":"You know, without them even calling, they'll get a lot of women volunteers."},{"time":179437,"text":"Then I used, tried to use the medical college girls."},{"time":182520,"text":"They also refused. Finally, I decide,"},{"time":185129,"text":"use sanitary pad myself."},{"time":187980,"text":"Now I am having a title like"},{"time":190111,"text":"the first man to set foot on the moon."},{"time":194288,"text":"Armstrong. Then Tenzing [and] Hillary, in Everest,"},{"time":197456,"text":"like that Muruganantham is the first man"},{"time":199345,"text":"wore a sanitary pad across the globe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203257,"text":"I wore a sanitary pad. I filled animal blood in a football bottle,"},{"time":206521,"text":"I tied it up here, there is a tube going into my panties,"},{"time":209207,"text":"while I'm walking, while I'm cycling, I made a press,"},{"time":211831,"text":"doses of blood will go there."},{"time":214147,"text":"That makes me bow down to any woman in front of me"},{"time":218175,"text":"to give full respect. That five days I'll never forget --"},{"time":221153,"text":"the messy days, the lousy days, that wetness."},{"time":223809,"text":"My God, it's unbelievable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229463,"text":"But here the problem is, one company is making napkin"},{"time":234224,"text":"out of cotton. It is working well."},{"time":236640,"text":"But I am also trying to make sanitary pad with the good cotton. It's not working."},{"time":239648,"text":"That makes me to want to refuse to continue this research and research and research."},{"time":243232,"text":"You need first funds."},{"time":244933,"text":"Not only financial crises, but because of the sanitary pad research,"},{"time":248251,"text":"I come through all sorts of problems, including"},{"time":251967,"text":"a divorce notice from my wife."},{"time":254370,"text":"Why is this? I used medical college girls."},{"time":257465,"text":"She suspects I am using as a trump card"},{"time":260319,"text":"to run behind medical college girls."},{"time":262775,"text":"Finally, I came to know it is a special cellulose"},{"time":266018,"text":"derived from a pinewood, but even after that,"},{"time":268426,"text":"you need a multimillion-dollar plant like this"},{"time":270428,"text":"to process that material. Again, a stop-up."},{"time":273790,"text":"Then I spend another four years to create my own"},{"time":277552,"text":"machine tools, a simple machine tool like this."},{"time":280215,"text":"In this machine, any rural woman can apply the same"},{"time":283459,"text":"raw materials that they are processing in the multinational plant,"},{"time":286303,"text":"anyone can make a world-class napkin at your dining hall."},{"time":289995,"text":"That is my invention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293212,"text":"So after that, what I did,"},{"time":295935,"text":"usually if anyone got a patent or an invention,"},{"time":299398,"text":"immediately you want to make, convert into this."},{"time":302941,"text":"I never did this. I dropped it just like this,"},{"time":305991,"text":"because you do this, if anyone runs after money,"},{"time":309575,"text":"their life will not [have] any beauty. It is boredom."},{"time":313292,"text":"A lot of people making a lot of money, billion,"},{"time":315303,"text":"billions of dollars accumulating."},{"time":317457,"text":"Why are they coming for, finally, for philanthropy?"},{"time":319703,"text":"Why the need for accumulating money, then doing philanthropy?"},{"time":323220,"text":"What if one decided to start philanthropy from the day one?"},{"time":326529,"text":"That's why I am giving this machine"},{"time":330077,"text":"only in rural India, for rural women, because in India,"},{"time":334015,"text":"[you'll be] surprised, only two percent of women"},{"time":336491,"text":"are using sanitary pads. The rest, they're using a rag cloth,"},{"time":339832,"text":"a leaf, husk, [saw] dust, everything except sanitary pads."},{"time":343692,"text":"It is the same in the 21st century. That's why I am going"},{"time":346079,"text":"to decide to give this machine only for poor women across India."},{"time":349620,"text":"So far, 630 installations happened in 23 states"},{"time":353001,"text":"in six other countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355637,"text":"Now I'm on my seventh year sustaining against"},{"time":360119,"text":"multinational, transnational giants -- makes all MBA students a question mark."},{"time":365137,"text":"A school dropout from Coimbatore, how he is able to sustaining?"},{"time":368422,"text":"That makes me a visiting professor and guest lecturer in all IIMs."},{"time":374522,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":379685,"text":"Play video one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":382530,"text":"(Video) Arunachalam Muruganantham: The thing I saw in my wife's hand, \"Why are you using that nasty cloth?\""},{"time":387702,"text":"She replied immediately, \"I know about napkins, but if I start"},{"time":392015,"text":"using napkins, then we have to cut our family milk budget.\""},{"time":395914,"text":"Why not make myself a low-cost napkin?"},{"time":400335,"text":"So I decided I'm going to sell this new machine"},{"time":403116,"text":"only for Women Self Help Groups."},{"time":409976,"text":"That is my idea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":414429,"text":"AM: And previously, you need a multimillion investment"},{"time":419144,"text":"for machine and all. Now, any rural woman can."},{"time":422644,"text":"They are performing puja."},{"time":424513,"text":"(Video): (Singing)"},{"time":441527,"text":"You just think, competing giants,"},{"time":446113,"text":"even from Harvard, Oxford, is difficult."},{"time":448004,"text":"I make a rural woman to compete with multinationals."},{"time":450888,"text":"I'm sustaining on seventh year."},{"time":452458,"text":"Already 600 installations. What is my mission?"},{"time":454719,"text":"I'm going to make India"},{"time":456580,"text":"[into] a 100-percent-sanitary-napkin-using country in my lifetime."},{"time":460584,"text":"In this way I'm going to provide not less than a million"},{"time":462569,"text":"rural employment that I'm going to create."},{"time":464627,"text":"That's why I'm not running after this bloody money."},{"time":468183,"text":"I'm doing something serious."},{"time":469683,"text":"If you chase a girl, the girl won't like you."},{"time":474032,"text":"Do your job simply, the girl will chase you."},{"time":476430,"text":"Like that, I never chased Mahalakshmi."},{"time":478781,"text":"Mahalakshmi is chasing me, I am keeping in the back pocket."},{"time":483651,"text":"Not in front pocket. I'm a back pocket man."},{"time":488107,"text":"That's all. A school dropout saw your problem in the society"},{"time":491679,"text":"of not using sanitary pad."},{"time":493711,"text":"I am becoming a solution provider. I'm very happy."},{"time":496011,"text":"I don't want to make this as a corporate entity."},{"time":498854,"text":"I want to make this as a local sanitary pad movement"},{"time":502857,"text":"across the globe. That's why I put all the details"},{"time":505710,"text":"on public domain like an open software."},{"time":509074,"text":"Now 110 countries are accessing it. Okay?"},{"time":513636,"text":"So I classify the people into three:"},{"time":517636,"text":"uneducated, little educated, surplus educated."},{"time":524558,"text":"Little educated, done this. Surplus educated,"},{"time":528449,"text":"what are you going to do for the society?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":529853,"text":"Thank you very much. Bye!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":533620,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}